STATUS_zh: 湯：判決類型：蔬菜外觀：夢幻般的質地：味道好：總體貧窮：可食用但不愉快的概要：這是一個很棒的湯，它充滿了顏色，健康的蔬菜和奶油！如果你不餓，這湯子你會感覺良好！然而，如果吃的是你的東西，應該避免這種湯。我還有3份湯 - 任何接受者？只有P＆P支付！享受！

STATUS: found that you can tell roughly where you are on the canal by the accents of the people who say hello!
STATUS_zh: 發現你可以通過打招呼的人的口音，大致告訴你在運河上。

STATUS: has just attended his first parish council meeting!
STATUS_zh: 剛剛參加了他的第一個教區委員會會議！

STATUS: regrets that he might have to dispose of his pumpkin (*PROPNAME*) as he is becoming a little furry and wonders if giving him a quick shave might do the job
STATUS_zh: 遺憾的是，他可能需要處理他的南瓜（*普遍*），因為他正在成為一個小毛茸茸，如果給他一個快速刮鬍子可能會做這項工作

STATUS: is now a graduate
STATUS_zh: 現在是畢業生

STATUS: has a huge pile of washing!
STATUS_zh: 有一堆巨大的洗衣！

STATUS: Why doesn't social interview ask me any questions... I feel very left out. :(
STATUS_zh: 為什麼社會面試不問我任何問題......我覺得很遺漏。 :(

STATUS: hasn't been outside yet today but is now going to post a letter to one lucky recipient!
STATUS_zh: 今天還沒有以外的地方，但現在正在發布一封幸運收件人的信！

STATUS: Is it just me or does anyone else feel in the mood for an ABBA sing along session?
STATUS_zh: 這只是我還是別人對ABBA沿著會議唱歌的情緒？

STATUS: is missing Katie
STATUS_zh: 缺少凱蒂

STATUS: realised at around 5 last night that he had nothing to offer to trick-or-treaters so he made toffee... but then nobody came.
STATUS_zh: 昨晚在左右5歲地實現，他沒有任何東西給欺騙或治療者提供，所以他製作了太妃糖......但是沒有人來。

STATUS: is soon to become a member of the con club!! Whoop!
STATUS_zh: 很快就成為了騙局俱樂部的成員！哎呀！

STATUS: no longer has a huge pile of washing
STATUS_zh: 不再有一堆巨大的洗滌

STATUS: doesn't know where anyone is!
STATUS_zh: 不知道任何人都在哪裡！

STATUS: What a busy morning! We had a plumber, the cleaner a dog walker and the gardener all around all at same time!
STATUS_zh: 什麼忙碌的早晨！我們有一個水管工，乾淨的狗助行器和園丁各處都在一起！

STATUS: is wondering how much tiffin cake he needs to eat to get one of his five a day fruit portions
STATUS_zh: 想知道他需要吃多少蒂蛋糕蛋糕，以獲得他五個果實的五個水果部分

STATUS: thinks 3D glasses make the world a little bit more fun!
STATUS_zh: 認為3D眼鏡讓世界變得有點樂趣！

STATUS: Last night I went to a conference where the police were asking us to pray for them. Lets pray for the police and our communities. God moves when his people pray.
STATUS_zh: 昨晚我去了一個警察要求我們為他們祈禱的會議。讓我們祈禱警察和我們的社區。當他的人民祈禱時，上帝搬家。

STATUS: apologises if he appears to be shouting or talking very loudly to people at the moment. He's getting used to talking to someone who is hard of hearing but keeps forgetting to talk normally to other people.
STATUS_zh: 如果他似乎喊叫或對目前的人大聲說話，請道歉。他習慣於與那些難以聽到的人交談，而是讓忘記忘記談論其他人。

STATUS: wants to know if anyone has borrowed an elf costume off him
STATUS_zh: 想知道有人是否借給他的精靈服裝

STATUS: is talking to *PROPNAME* :D
STATUS_zh: 正在與* propname *：d

STATUS: is off to practice being a shepherd
STATUS_zh: 練習是牧羊人

STATUS: has been put on hold but is enjoying (dancing to) the music! :D
STATUS_zh: 已被擱置但正在享受（跳舞）音樂！ ：D.

STATUS: is moving yet more wood!
STATUS_zh: 正在移動更多的木頭！

STATUS: Yaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaay Snooooooooooooooow!
STATUS_zh: Yaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaay snooooooooooooow！

STATUS: may have just slipped over on the ice but thinks he got away with it by making it look like he was break dancing...
STATUS_zh: 可能只是在冰上滑倒，但思考他通過使它看起來像是霹靂舞......

STATUS: is heading home for Christmas!
STATUS_zh: 是聖誕節的回家！

STATUS: may have eaten a few too many sweets today...
STATUS_zh: 今天可能已經吃了一些太多醣果......

STATUS: is fighting to make it to the table football semis
STATUS_zh: 正在戰鬥，以便將其發作為桌子足球半決賽

STATUS: finds it highly amusing that we are currently bringing the milk inside to warm it up in the fridge!
STATUS_zh: 發現我們目前帶著裡面帶內牛奶在冰箱裡加熱它的非常有趣。

STATUS: is about to start wrapping Christmas presents!
STATUS_zh: 即將開始包裝聖誕禮物！

STATUS: is no longer talking to *PROPNAME* - but not in a bad way. Just because it is impractical and expensive to talk on the phone continuously and because we both needed to do things.
STATUS_zh: 不再與* propname *說話 - 但不是以糟糕的方式。僅僅因為它不斷地在手機上談話是不切實際和昂貴的，因為我們都需要做事。

STATUS: Writing, then 2 chapters homework, then bed. Or just Loveline ?
STATUS_zh: 寫作，然後是2章作業，然後睡覺。或只是Lovelele？

STATUS: My mind is so confusing, it's scary.
STATUS_zh: 我的思緒令人困惑，這是可怕的。

STATUS: I just....I can't do this without family...friends. Anybody ?
STATUS_zh: 我只是......我不能在沒有家人的情況下這樣做......朋友。有人嗎？

STATUS: Getting together map, snacks, music, and up-all-night accessories for Hollywood. Will starting driving at 4 am.
STATUS_zh: 為好萊塢聚集在一起地圖，小吃，音樂和全夜配件。將在凌晨4點開始開車。

STATUS: Loveline, pills, and a kitty. Best combo ever. night.
STATUS_zh: Loveline，藥片和貓咪。有史以來最好的組合。夜晚。

STATUS: Fucking hell, grrrr....
STATUS_zh: 他媽的地獄，grrrr ....

STATUS: Gah, head's pounding. I wish I wasn't in so much pain. It makes the pills that much more tempting...
STATUS_zh: Gah，頭的砰砰聲。我希望我不太痛苦。它使藥丸更誘人......

STATUS: Okay, so what are the different plans for Friday night in LA ? There's *PROPNAME*...?
STATUS_zh: 好的，那麼星期五晚上在洛杉磯的不同計劃是什麼？有* propname * ......？

STATUS: Some people say pain can be controlled by the mind. I do not agree with these people. It doesn't mean I don't admire them though.
STATUS_zh: 有些人說痛苦可以由心靈控制。我不同意這些人。這並不意味著我不羨慕他們。

STATUS: Doctors seem to want me to sit out. In a wheelchair...no fucking way. I'd rather walk down the street with tears streaming, than be benched....which, unfortunately, is not too far off.
STATUS_zh: 醫生似乎希望我坐下來。在輪椅上......沒有他媽的。我寧願走下淚流滿面的街道，而不是坐在地上......不幸的是，這不太遙遠。

STATUS: Well anyway, fuck it. I'm gonna die young but happy. Rather than healthy and old.
STATUS_zh: 無論如何，他媽的他媽的。我會死年輕但快樂。而不是健康和舊的。

STATUS: Gonna be 83 degree today ! Coffee, sunshine, and sweet email from a friend. Day started with love, is continuing, and will end in love.
STATUS_zh: 今天要83度！來自朋友的咖啡，陽光和甜蜜的電子郵件。一天開始愛，正在繼續，並將結束戀愛。

STATUS: Home...finally. Sooooo tired...gonna get a couple hours before work starts up again.
STATUS_zh: 家......最後。 Sooooo累了......在工作再次開始之前，會在幾個小時內完成。

STATUS: Alright, recharged as it were. If this is a night of no dark dreams; you are a miracle worker too.
STATUS_zh: 好吧，按照它充電。如果這是一個沒有黑暗夢想的夜晚;你也是一個奇蹟。

STATUS: Easy to read; I like that !
STATUS_zh: 易於閱讀;我喜歡 ！

STATUS: Sleeeeeeeeeep......
STATUS_zh: sleeeeeeeeeep ......

STATUS: I find I'm enjoying tiny poetry.  Such as: Rain- My ears hear a drip, drop, splash It's more of a scream, laugh, live And you make it so hard not to be cliche. You pile on my dreams,  Like power lines on a sky. Is it raining where you are ?
STATUS_zh: 我發現我很享受小詩歌。如：雨 - 我的耳朵聽到滴水，下降，飛濺它更像是一個尖叫，笑，生活，你使它變得如此努力，不要陳詞濫調。你堆在我的夢中，就像天空中的電力線一樣。下雨了嗎？

STATUS: Not tired, must sleep. Long week ahead, and no weekend. Friday is no longer a day off. Sore all over, but I asked for it. Cig, Loveline, sleep...smile, love, remember.
STATUS_zh: 不累，必須睡覺。漫長的一周，沒有周末。星期五不再休息一天。疼痛，但我要求它。 CIG，Loveline，睡覺......微笑，愛，記住。

STATUS: Today was a much needed day off !! Back to a fake smile tomorrow, but rejuvinated by friends tonight.
STATUS_zh: 今天是一個休息的一天！明天回到假的笑容，但今晚由朋友重新改造。

STATUS: It's moments like this that I wish I worked for Walmart. I hate rape. I'm no good at counseling "victims". Especially when it's a parental perpetrator. Why is this the way of the world ? Why is it reality ?
STATUS_zh: 這是我希望我為沃爾瑪工作的時刻。我討厭強姦。我不擅長諮詢“受害者”。特別是當它是父母的犯罪者時。為什麼這是世界的方式？為什麼它是現實？

STATUS: Blah ! Work lots, need money. Not worth it really. I'm loosing the happiness !!
STATUS_zh: ！！工作很多，需要錢。真的不值得。我失去了幸福！

STATUS: Sore throat starting out. Tempted to gargle vodka, but must get some work done.
STATUS_zh: 喉嚨痛開始。誘惑漱口伏特加，但必須完成一些工作。

STATUS: Frustrated beyond all hell, blog isn't helping.
STATUS_zh: 沮喪超越了所有地獄，博客沒有幫助。

STATUS: "I've been high, and I've been down, my head in the clouds and my hands on the ground. "
STATUS_zh: “我一直很高，我一直在下來，我的頭在雲端和我的手上。”

STATUS: I think I would be dead without my heating pad. I am completely serious.
STATUS_zh: 沒有我的加熱墊，我想我會死。我完全認真。

STATUS: I don't know where my mind is in this moment. It's so fleeting; emotion. I'm so tired, but I can't sleep. And like *PROPNAME* says, a shotgun just leaves a messed up wall.  Ah well. Random thoughts. Better go to bed before that crap goes deeper.
STATUS_zh: 我不知道我在這一刻在哪裡。這是如此短暫;情感。我很累，但我無法入睡。喜歡* probname *說，一個霰彈槍只是留下了一個陷入困境的牆壁。呃，好吧。隨機思想。在垃圾更深的地方之前，最好去睡覺。

STATUS: Gah, headache. Okay my body's failing me; I'm going to put off work 'til tomorrow and take care of myself now. Ice cream, giant sweater, warm bed...I'm comin'.
STATUS_zh: gah，頭痛。好吧，我的身體失敗了;我明天要去下班，現在照顧好自己。冰淇淋，巨型毛衣，溫暖的床......我正在進行'。

STATUS: Okay, people, seriously..."lol" is so blood annoying when you use it on every line.
STATUS_zh: 好的，人們，認真地......“哈哈”是在每一行使用時煩惱的血液煩人。

STATUS: Fuck. Okay, file another tragic story in a box of my mind to be dealt with when I no longer have a heart. Wonder how much longer it'll take...not too long now.
STATUS_zh: 他媽的。好的，在我不再有一顆心臟的時候，在我的一盒中提交另一個悲劇性的故事。想知道它有多長，現在不算太久。

STATUS: Okay, I'm no good at positivity right now. That's my work "hat". So sue me.
STATUS_zh: 好的，我現在不擅長積極性。那是我的工作“帽子”。所以起訴我。

STATUS: Ah coffee....makes the world go 'round.
STATUS_zh: 啊咖啡......讓世界變得圓滿。

STATUS: I feel emptied out; please rain down on me...darkness and light, come fill me up.
STATUS_zh: 我覺得清空了;請下雨......黑暗和光線，來填滿我。

STATUS: Okay, must sleep. Must work in mere hours...ah who am I kidding ? I don't sleep. Or eat. Just smoke...and work. And love.
STATUS_zh: 好的，必須睡覺。必須在幾個小時內工作......我在開玩笑誰？我不睡覺。或吃。只是抽煙......和工作。和愛。

STATUS: Got the new iPhone 3GS. Don't ask how, I won't tell you. But thank you.
STATUS_zh: 得到了新的iphone 3gs。不要問怎麼樣，我不會告訴你。但謝謝。

STATUS: "I like my chicken fried, a cold beer on a friday night, a pair of jeans that fit just right, and the radio up !"
STATUS_zh: “我喜歡我的雞肉，星期五晚上炒一杯冰鎮啤酒，一對牛仔褲合適，吧台吧！”

STATUS: QTD: "'Flower' usually refers to a vulva in general, not virginity or 'cherry popping' as the kids would say." Hahahaha
STATUS_zh: QTD：“Flower'通常是指一般的外陰，而不是孩子們會說的童貞或”櫻桃爆裂“。”哈哈哈哈

STATUS: "Little red bird under a chair, waiting for the crumbs to fall. Daddy said, 'Get a job'. Well don't you see, Daddy, how good I am at catching crumbs ?"
STATUS_zh: “椅子下面的小紅鳥，等待碎屑落下。爸爸說，”找工作“。難道你不知道，爸爸，我在捕獲麵包屑時有多好？”

STATUS: Aggrevated that I let someone else take me from really happy to hurt and depressed. It's on me to change my reaction to be one of Loveful Me.
STATUS_zh: 僵局，我讓別人帶我從真正幸福地傷害和沮喪。改變我的反應是我的反應，成為一個愛我的反應。

STATUS: I need to be asleep. I get up in....5 hrs ? No idea really. What am I doing again ?
STATUS_zh: 我需要睡著了。我站在...... 5小時？真的不知道。我又做了什麼？

STATUS: "For a moment I love everything I see and think and feel..."
STATUS_zh: “有了一會兒，我喜歡我所看到的一切和思考和感受......”

STATUS: "Walking by the river I...reach my hands to cup the sky. It runs down my arms...a bitter blue. Turn to red, and the gashes grew." God, this song...every word is raw and honest.
STATUS_zh: “在河邊散步......到達我的手杯子天空。它沿著我的手臂跑去......一個苦澀的藍色。轉向紅色，而怪物增長。”上帝，這首歌......每一個詞都是原始的，誠實。

STATUS: I am what I make of myself. I am Love. I am.
STATUS_zh: 我是我自己所做的。我是愛。我是。

STATUS: I wish I was in NYC and seeing *PROPNAME* tomorrow night....
STATUS_zh: 我希望我在紐約，看看*假單*明天晚上....

STATUS: I need to go back to my live food diet. Not 90% like before, but I bet I could do 75% without losing too much weight..
STATUS_zh: 我需要回到我的活飲食。之前沒有90％，但我打賭我可以做75％而不會失去太多重量..

STATUS: It's ugly here. But there are sparks...moments. Love.
STATUS_zh: 這是醜陋的。但有火花......時刻。愛。

STATUS: I guess it all depends on your mood...why can't these meds be any damn good ?
STATUS_zh: 我猜這一切都取決於你的心情......為什麼這些藥片不能成為任何該死的？

STATUS: "I believe in love. It's just my heart that keeps turning me down. I believe in love, I think it's just fine."
STATUS_zh: “我相信愛情。這只是我的心讓我失望。我相信愛情，我認為這很好。”

STATUS: I always want the blog to be the magical valve. Turn it on, write, be healed. It never is though. And now I still hurt, I just feel more raw now. As long as I stay with the emotion and don't deny...I'll be alright.
STATUS_zh: 我總是希望博客成為神奇的閥門。打開它，寫，癒合。它永遠不會。現在我仍然受傷了，我現在感覺更加原始。只要我留在情感而不是否認......我會沒事的。

STATUS: Fucking musicians. Fuck musicians...
STATUS_zh: 他媽的音樂家。他媽的音樂家......

STATUS: Now that I'm done writing, I need food...hmmm....
STATUS_zh: 現在我完成了寫作，我需要食物......嗯....

STATUS: I did that shit with spasms, AND after 8 shots of espresso today. WHO DA MAN ?? Beauty school, here I come...right after this next Criminal Minds. <3
STATUS_zh: 我用痙攣落下了這件狗屎，今天8次拍攝後。誰是男人？美容學校，在這裡我來......在這個下一個犯罪頭腦之後。 <3

STATUS: I have to find the superhero I use to be. I can't bring myself to believe it was just the Love of a silly boy that did it.
STATUS_zh: 我必須找到我用的超級英雄。我不能讓自己相信它只是對那個愚蠢的男孩的愛。

STATUS: (Breast cancer awareness question - what colour bra are you wearing ?) No colour. I'm not a fan of bras lately. But this is a stupid FB idea. It doesn't really raise awareness unless you also say what the hell it's about !  Stupid, stupid.
STATUS_zh: （乳腺癌意識問題 - 你穿什麼顏色的胸罩？）沒有顏色。我最近不是胸罩的粉絲。但這是一個愚蠢的fb想法。除非你也說出這是關於的，否則並沒有真正提高認識！愚蠢，愚蠢。

STATUS: My most awesome friend just surprise-attacked me with a present of a dark chocolate bacon bar...drool. Best. Moment. Ever.
STATUS_zh: 我最棒的朋友只是驚訝地襲擊了我的黑巧克力培根吧......流口水。最好的。片刻。曾經。

STATUS: Again, my company and night are ruined by some physical ailment of mine. I am fucking tired of it.
STATUS_zh: 再次，我的公司和夜晚被我的一些身體疾病毀了。我他媽的厭倦了它。

STATUS: Wow, fresh air. Crazy. Good day sunshine, you're my favourite star.
STATUS_zh: 哇，新鮮空氣。瘋狂的。美好的一天陽光，你是我最喜歡的明星。

STATUS: Okay, sleep. Dreaming of bacon and dark chocolate. mmmm....
STATUS_zh: 好的，睡覺。夢見培根和黑巧克力。 mmmm ....

STATUS: To be something I am not...that is what I'll be when I grow up. God, it'll be stunning.
STATUS_zh: 成為我不是......這就是我長大的時候我會成為什麼樣的。上帝，它會令人驚嘆。

STATUS: Okay. Maybe not sleep.
STATUS_zh: 好的。也許不睡覺。

STATUS: Pain is a bitch.
STATUS_zh: 疼痛是婊子。

STATUS: Got called in to work tomorrow. At least I don't have to run groups. Bed early tonight.
STATUS_zh: 明天被打電話去上班。至少我不必運行組。今晚睡覺。

STATUS: Wow been a tiring and painful day. Gonna set up a movie and try to relax. Love to all of my beautiful friends and family for the support and awesomeness of who they are. And a high five to my Surgeon who is THE man and gives me hope of having a less painful life. <3 you all. You make me happy, yes YOU.
STATUS_zh: 哇是累人和痛苦的一天。會建立一部電影，並儘量放鬆身心。愛我所有美麗的朋友和家人的支持和令人敬畏。和我的外科醫生高五個是男人，讓我希望生活不那麼痛苦。 <3你們所有人。你讓我開心，是的。

STATUS: My most Awesome Surgeon says I can try walking today and if all goes well, I can work tomorrow !! YAY !! I'm gonna need the money if I wanna try and quit this job to focus on my other jobs//opportunities. Wish me luck on the walking ! I'll report back.
STATUS_zh: 我最棒的外科醫生說，我今天可以嘗試走路，如果一切順利，我明天可以工作！耶 ！！如果我想嘗試退出這份工作，我會努力專注於我的其他工作//機會。祝我走好走路！我會報告。

STATUS: Just ate a nice happy cow filet with red wine reduction. Wish my feet weren't throbbing so I could really cook !! Tomorrow we shall throw down...my 12-in skillet and me.
STATUS_zh: 只是吃了一個漂亮的牛絲絨，減少紅葡萄酒。祝我的腳沒有悸動，所以我真的可以做飯！明天我們會扔掉......我的12英寸煎鍋和我。

STATUS: Having surgery today. I can't wait to be in hospital. I'm not a big fan of surgery. But hospitals feel like home to me. Calming in the chaos.
STATUS_zh: 今天有手術。我迫不及待想在醫院。我不是手術的忠實粉絲。但醫院覺得自己喜歡我。鎮定在混亂中。

STATUS: Reading an amazing book called Stranger in a Strange Land. Now I'm listening to Loveline and trying to rest for the god-aweful full day tomorrow.
STATUS_zh: 在一個陌生的土地上讀一個名叫陌生人的驚人的書。現在我正在聽愛Loveline，並試圖明天為上帝享受令人敬畏的全天。

STATUS: Off to a training, not back til Sunday. So tired. So in pain. Starbucks will make it all better, I know it !

STATUS: I don't know how it all works. I don't know why. I don't know how. I just am who you made me. I have what you gave me. Let me be yours. Please take all I have as yours. STATUS: Whilst I may not understand the history behind thanksgiving, I can get behind any holiday that consists of a huge amount of food, alcohol and friends. Happy thanksgiving to my American friends. And to anyone else, today is just an excuse for us to take part in "cultural diversity" and get drunk and stuffed with lots of food.

STATUS: Hates facebook messaging, it always looks like you are waiting for the other person to message back, and then you see that it has infact timed out (again) and the person messaged back 6 hours ago. *sigh*

STATUS: is still living with your ghost, lonely and dreaming of the west coast. She just wants to feel some sunshine.

STATUS: I'm ecstatic! I just spoke briefly with *PROPNAME*'s lawyer. Based on some "case files" I emailed her, we have enough evidence to prove CPS's removal of the kids was illegal and grounds for an emergency hearing. We believe we have enough evidence to cost both CPS and Humble PD their "qualified immunity", allowing us to file a civil suit against them and the apartments. ANYONE KNOW A GOOD CIVIL ATTORNEY???

STATUS: Things went better. *PROPNAME* was able to retain her composur and not break down in court. The judge referred the case to "mediation". We go to that Jan 29th.

STATUS: Please keep *PROPNAME*'s family in your prayers tonight and tomorrow. We have to be in court at 9am. Really pray for the oldest *PROPNAME* went to his dad's for his summer visit and had his mother, brother and sister stripped from him for six months. CPS is providing Christmas for the other two but not him.  I sure hope we succeed at stripping them of their "immunity" and make them pay for what they've done to this family.
